						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/uncategorized/" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a></span>
						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/citigroup/" rel="tag">Citigroup</a></span>					</p>
