																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/05/31/kayak-to-delay-ipo-as-facebook-shares-sink-further-telegraph/#respond" title="Comment on Kayak to delay IPO as Facebook shares sink further&nbsp;[Telegraph]">Leave a comment</a></span>
