				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/05/31/uk-nanny-state-gets-milked-for-all-its-worth-sovereignman-com/">UK nanny state gets milked for all it’s worth [sovereignman.com]</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">May 31, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/05/31/uk-nanny-state-gets-milked-for-all-its-worth-sovereignman-com/#respond" title="Comment on UK nanny state gets milked for all it’s worth [sovereignman.com]">Leave a comment</a></span>
